## Integration with Assignments

### Question Selection
When building assignments, teachers can:
- Browse the question bank with filters
- Search by physics concepts
- Preview questions before adding
- Track which questions are most effective

### Usage Tracking
```typescript
// Increment usage count when question is added to assignment
await incrementUsageCount(questionId, assignmentId)
```

